{"tid":441462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特種警衞原來係筍工！4年加到萬七下周招生","createTime":"2017-10-19T16:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T10:42:26.000Z","uid":61155,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f67d1ad774cef30900a1c89093771dc75bd9b911","tid":441462,"uid":61155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"公開試失敗不代表一切，有同路人勉勵年青人「要嘗試第一步」，爭取不同工作機會。90後吳銘殷會考只有3分，曾經「做散工」接近4年，月入試過僅有7000港元，連家用也無能力支付。其後經家人要求而加入僱員再培訓局的「特種警衞訓練計劃」，4年過去，他現時已是一名高級警衞長，月薪近1.7萬港元。他勉勵其他年輕人要有責任心。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n「特種警衞訓練計劃」早於2013年推出，過去曾舉辦3屆，共有231名畢業生，當中97%畢業學員均能入職，而6個月內的留職比率更達80%。訓練計劃經過1年時間的檢討後，即將推出共160個名額的基礎證書(度身訂造課程)，現年18至24歲人士、完成中學課程即可報讀，而為期2個月的課程費用全免，學員完成課程後可獲1年實習，底薪為13,500港元，另外會按表現加1年約3000港元的「在職培訓津貼」，下周將有招生日。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n吳銘殷是計劃首屆「特種警衞」畢業生，他坦言，當時報讀計劃是為了滿足家人想他有穩定工作的要求，抱「做住先」的心態完成課程，但隨工作的晉升機會、環境及薪金調整等因素，現時希望繼續在行內發展。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n在會展擔任高級警衞長的吳表示，工作是要確保在展覽順利舉行，過往曾協助珠寶展等保安工作，而去年全國人大委員長張德江訪港的經驗則最深刻。他指，「第一次參與咁大型行動」，當時擔任會展正門的保安位置，心情非常緊張，沒想到自己可以參與其中，又笑稱工作福利包括看演唱會等活動，包括早前香港拳手曹星如的拳賽。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n他指，工作與「你平時係屋企樓下見到嘅保安」有大分別，現時主要在會展進行人流管制、保護要員等，有別於保安只看管住客出入。他認為，現時年輕人抱「想玩又想有錢」的心態，認為「如果真係唔嘗試第一步嘅話，大家都唔會見到今日嘅我」。&nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xngympwj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxngympwj&h=0a1ee809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cjrbplnh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcjrbplnh&h=fc402329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171016/bkn-20171016164800650-1016_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171016%2Fbkn-20171016164800650-1016_00822_001.html&d=F1z7SXG2p8x4ESv3wBiOqTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=20ac222c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171016/bkn-20171016164800650-1016_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n嘩7撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -保安？狗也不屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -又hea又有錢收，都唔錯嘅"},{"pid":"73bb42c6f8c05d38efcab0287b8bd543ed0b95da","tid":441462,"uid":10433,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"龍咁威？"},{"pid":"7b81e9f84d3da63eec072691b1175ad4c0a82166","tid":441462,"uid":61155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"寫到好似小學生第一日去做義工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96ac35b61a8ae222024ef12ec82bb9caa05d9a5","tid":441462,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫到好似小學生第一日去做義工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n龍咁威wo"},{"pid":"441e8f313094ec3438edc1635d3506acac8c08c8","tid":441462,"uid":61155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"會考3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99769a9935fdf1e0ce8adaec09118f94b1eff52e","tid":441462,"uid":42314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"4年冇20k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e370d7a69bbd0c31e83e8aa12fb158152df446e9","tid":441462,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4年冇20k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr