\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋保護要員？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正既要員會唔會搵你班只係再培訓左兩個月既蛋散保護呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw件制服紫色好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f85a6f661b65f858328927dbcc2da910cb66d32","tid":441462,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:34:50.000Z","msg":"工時幾多先得架, 返足6日每日12個鐘呀?"},{"pid":"72fd52b35f0e62f70908a3167060b2f9f727d30c","tid":441462,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:36:00.000Z","msg":"4年夠讀到張top up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee6f37981f17f58a61db0c9b25602fd50854b36","tid":441462,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工時幾多先得架, 返足6日每日12個鐘呀?</blockquote><br />\n可能係,隨時仲要外判合約"}]}